02:45.960 --> 02:51.560
They [don't like] us. Portugese people don't take care of us they say.

02:51.960 --> 02:52.560
Don't take?

02:52.800 --> 02:56.080
Don't take care of us when they were in France.

02:56.400 --> 03:00.320
Things like that.

03:00.520 --> 03:01.360
They say, Mother...

03:01.560 --> 03:02.080
Yeah?

03:02.280 --> 03:07.160
They say "what happens if we don't push ourselves" and want us to take,

03:07.480 --> 03:11.000
I'm not used to take baths but that they don't like it.

03:11.640 --> 03:12.640
French people say so?

03:12.840 --> 03:13.560
Yes, Mother.

