03:16.800 --> 03:18.320
No, I don't know.

03:18.680 --> 03:22.440
It's racialism Mother, just racialism.

03:23.800 --> 03:27.880
Portugese are much more clean thaan French are.

03:28.520 --> 03:29.640
What are they talking?

03:29.880 --> 03:30.720
I don't know.

03:31.040 --> 03:36.280
Horrible, they are digging it up.

03:37.200 --> 03:39.840
No morals, nothing. All bathrooms.

03:43.040 --> 03:44.880
That's why they are always perfumering.

03:51.040 --> 03:54.160
Now that they say that about Portugese. Sometimes I can't believe it.

04:03.560 --> 04:05.960
All racialism. It's very clear.

04:14.920 --> 04:16.960
That too are very concerned Indian people

04:17.440 --> 04:23.480
who are I mean really used to, say, take baths in India. That's true.

04:24.880 --> 04:29.240
They are very clean and, but otherwise everywhere,

04:30.040 --> 04:32.520
the whole of you are not. It's just the same.

04:32.720 --> 04:34.880
Worst is France, worst.

