08:37.480 --> 08:39.480
they don't have so much of racialism.

08:40.520 --> 08:43.760
They have only for blacks and whites but otherwise they don't have.

08:44.600 --> 08:47.680
Even blacks and whites it is not so much [uprised] we see it in England.

08:48.320 --> 08:52.040
Not so sharp. They have crossed that quite a lot.

08:52.520 --> 08:53.640
They are very cosmopolite.

08:57.280 --> 08:59.960
That's something creditable to them.

09:03.400 --> 09:06.840
In America you'll find so many races, all kind.

09:07.120 --> 09:09.160
Indians are treated very well.

09:09.720 --> 09:11.880
Not the way they are treated in England.

09:16.080 --> 09:20.920
Italians, also. So many Italians have shops. Yes.

