Now you make some tea for Me?

09:25.760 --> 09:27.840
Make some tea for Me.

09:32.320 --> 09:34.520
I think that some food will be for children.

09:36.360 --> 09:37.480
Good.

09:38.680 --> 09:40.560
He taught you. Press it.

09:57.680 --> 09:58.800
He's sturdy and good.

10:03.440 --> 10:06.760
But Italians are such craftsmen and such artists.

10:08.040 --> 10:10.760
What do they think of themselves? French.

10:12.080 --> 10:13.600
I don't know Mother.

10:14.360 --> 10:16.840
Maybe they are jealous, because

10:17.040 --> 10:20.120
Italians when they work they are very clever, with the hands and...

10:20.320 --> 10:23.880
With the hands, with art. And with paintings.

10:24.680 --> 10:30.480
Designing, for designing they are very good.

10:31.520 --> 10:34.400
The quality also of all these things, are very good quality.

10:34.600 --> 10:35.680
And even today it is good.

10:35.920 --> 10:37.200
Yes, yes.

10:38.200 --> 10:40.440
I don't know why, why French have this kind of a...

10:40.640 --> 10:42.880
Because they import by the, the Italian's fault is

10:43.080 --> 10:45.800
better achievements and the French just don't like it.

10:46.360 --> 10:47.560
That's it. Jealousy.

10:47.920 --> 10:49.040
Yeah.

10:49.240 --> 10:51.760
All, all salesmen in fact, they say "Oh, Italian products,

10:52.080 --> 10:53.480
they are fine products,

10:53.760 --> 10:56.120
we are going to trade with these because it's cheaper then".

10:56.320 --> 11:03.120
And the French you know don't like that because it wouldn't be good for their bussiness.

11:03.320 --> 11:05.960
Yes. Where is the cover?

11:10.240 --> 11:13.040
There's a little cover attached inside.

11:17.120 --> 11:19.880
How they are changed with little things you see.

11:20.600 --> 11:26.600
I wish human beings were like that, so simple.

