Did you hear?

11:45.999 --> 11:47.440
No I didn't know.

11:48.800 --> 11:53.960
And her husband, you see now, is [future Prime Minister].

11:54.160 --> 11:55.800
Indira Gandhi always thinks that

11:56.400 --> 11:59.200
she should make her children the Prime Ministers,

11:59.400 --> 12:01.160
thinks it's her father's property.

12:02.320 --> 12:05.800
So now she's trying to put him up as a Prime Minister.

12:06.800 --> 12:09.080
His wife is an Italian.

12:10.360 --> 12:12.800
Sonia, her name is Sonia.

12:15.760 --> 12:18.680
It's an Indian name, Sonia. I don't know what it means in Italy?

