No, it's a name. They also...

12:22.080 --> 12:26.720
Sorry, I don't know what it means but people's name is Sonia.

12:27.240 --> 12:35.000
But in Italy, they are giving rather international names like that...[unclear]

12:35.320 --> 12:36.240
It's Indian name.

12:36.440 --> 12:36.920
Sonia? Yes.

12:37.120 --> 12:39.960
Sonia it's Indian name, actually. See,

12:41.440 --> 12:44.560
like our Sonu, and I'll tell to Miss Ramani, Gavin Pallav Sonu,

12:44.920 --> 12:48.240
and out of love we'll call Sonia, out of love, you see, like that.

12:53.240 --> 12:58.440
Just like that. But that is now taken there like, Sonia.

12:58.680 --> 13:00.520
I was surprised, it's an Indian name.

