47:43.240 --> 47:46.920
the man who is going to helps us is dr. Marva. He says that

47:47.120 --> 47:51.080
he knows many people here and he will arrange a TV and everything,

47:52.320 --> 47:57.080
in Los Angeles. And see now, he's become the Mare of Los Angeles.

47:57.920 --> 47:59.840
Oh, great.

48:04.440 --> 48:06.880
What help we get.

48:08.400 --> 48:11.640
But despite all that as you told Me about that

48:13.520 --> 48:16.400
many [crawling in], despite all that,

48:18.080 --> 48:21.000
human beings are the ones who will get this done.

48:22.800 --> 48:25.320
Whatever we may try, God has find His level best,

48:26.200 --> 48:29.600
to do this and to do that, everything. Same thing in New York.

48:30.720 --> 48:34.800
There was one dr. Lanjeevan whom I met and he wanted Me,

48:35.720 --> 48:37.920
somehow or another to talk to doctors and all that.

48:38.680 --> 48:44.160
But he said, "I don't know, I feel they don't listen to me and all that".

48:45.600 --> 48:48.960
And he became the chairman, chairman

48:49.400 --> 48:53.880
of all the practicing doctors of New York, that association.

48:54.800 --> 48:56.560
But then he refused to do anything for Me.

48:58.600 --> 49:03.120
And next year lost his job, got into trouble, everything he had.

49:03.720 --> 49:07.360
But he became the chairman and refused to do anything for Me.

49:07.560 --> 49:09.400
Then he had problems.

49:18.560 --> 49:25.720
So nature, even God's help, everything is perfect. You can't blame it.

49:27.680 --> 49:30.480
The earnestness of Sahaja Yoghis, their desire,

49:31.560 --> 49:33.760
to get so many to Sahaja Yoga. Everything is there.

49:34.840 --> 49:38.280
But somehow the negative forces are so active,

49:39.600 --> 49:42.800
that human beings you see, they can't see things through.

49:44.400 --> 49:47.240
It's very sad. What's going to happen to all these people?

49:48.480 --> 49:51.240
They don't know they will go to hell and hell is so horrid.

49:53.000 --> 49:54.120
There's no other way out.

50:08.440 --> 50:11.320
I mean I can go to any extent to please them, to do what they want

50:11.520 --> 50:14.120
but they must get their Realization.

50:35.480 --> 50:37.400
There's somebody who wanted to meet Me.

50:39.160 --> 50:44.280
So C.P. said, "He must come and see You. You are a saint.

50:46.040 --> 50:48.040
He's coming to see you as a saint. He should come and see You.

50:48.280 --> 50:51.520
Why should You go and see him? I said, "Baba, it doesn't matter.

50:52.280 --> 50:54.480
But if it will help Sahaja Yoga I will go and see him.

50:55.120 --> 50:56.880
I don't mind, I have no dignity, nothing.

50:57.280 --> 51:00.360
I'll just go and see the fellow if it works out for good".

51:02.840 --> 51:06.680
But no... Trying.

51:30.400 --> 51:31.720
Such help, you can't imagine.

51:35.200 --> 51:41.400
I was in Bangalore and he was a yoga teacher.

51:45.440 --> 51:48.600
And he came to Me and he started to talk

51:50.640 --> 51:53.520
and as usually he became rather rude. He said,

51:54.000 --> 51:55.880
"But why should you say that You have got Realization?

51:56.080 --> 51:58.560
Why should You say that You can raise the Kundalini?"

51:59.120 --> 52:00.720
I said, "I never say".

52:01.840 --> 52:05.320
Because one of his assistants,

52:05.960 --> 52:08.280
had come to Me so I said, " I've never told her".

52:08.999 --> 52:12.440
She knows about Me, so many people know. Ask her.

52:13.640 --> 52:16.880
At that time only who comes in,

52:17.720 --> 52:24.760
is the Secretary of the President of India, whom I have cured.

52:25.680 --> 52:30.840
He just jumped on him. He said, " You are a very rude and arrogant fellow".

52:31.480 --> 52:32.920
What do you mean by saying such things to Her?

52:33.200 --> 52:35.280
Do you know what She has done, who is She?

52:35.480 --> 52:37.400
Who are you? Why should you ask such a question?

52:37.960 --> 52:39.240
He just jumped on him.

52:41.240 --> 52:44.280
Very rude and arrogant person. What do you mean by saying these things?

52:44.520 --> 52:46.760
What autority you have to say such things to Her?

52:47.720 --> 52:49.960
Do you know She's cured our president. I've seen it with my eyes.

52:50.160 --> 52:52.280
She's cured one man and I've seen it.

52:52.600 --> 52:57.240
It was remarcable because we, form was very interested itself, doesn't matter.

52:58.080 --> 53:01.920
But there is a beautiful church

53:02.920 --> 53:05.480
and when you go through the church you have to go down,

53:06.920 --> 53:13.600
and there you find, there is a little statue, of Mother of Christ.

53:14.520 --> 53:18.999
The face is exactly like Mine. Is put there.

